{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/BufferedInputStreamSignalName"]]},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"its value set through "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set()"},{"type":"text","text":", et al."}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"case","roleHeading":"Case","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"notify"}],"title":"BufferedInputStreamSignalName.notify","externalID":"s:3GIO29BufferedInputStreamSignalNameO6notifyyA2CmF"},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/bufferedinputstreamsignalname\/notify"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"notify","kind":"identifier"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then any call to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":" results"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"n